    "Therefore, the accuracy of the AI detection systems was no better than chance.",
    "The AI detection systems exhibited limited abilities to correctly detect authorship, at least for short texts generated by AI.",
    "A regression analysis was conducted to examine the correlation between the accuracy of the AI detection systems and the accuracy of the participants.",
